 People visit the Italian wine exhibition area during the 105th China Food & Drinks Fair in the national convention and exhibition center in Tianjin, north China, Oct. 20, 2021. Candido Mormile, an owner and founder of a wineries association from Italy, Lunanera Italian winery association, gets a good result and meets new cooperations in the 105th China Food & Drinks Fair. The fair kicked off on Tuesday in Tianjin Municipality, attracting more than 3,000 exhibitors. (Xinhua/Sun Fanyue)  